  <brief_title>Ph2a Study to Evaluate IW-3718 in Patients With Gastroesophageal Reflux Not Completely Responsive to Proton Pump Inhibitors</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2a Study to Evaluate the Effect of IW-3718 Administered Orally for 4 Weeks in Patients With GERD Not Completely Responsive to Proton Pump Inhibitors</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
